          logo</a> is a trademark of npm, Inc.
        li.
          <a href="http://webcomponents.org/">Web components logo</a> from the
          webcomponents.org contributors.
        li.
          <a href="http://nodejs.org/logos/">Node.js</a> is a trademark of
          Joyent, Inc.

